{"tid":1838753,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個係乜L野香港","createTime":"2020-01-24T06:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T14:26:30.000Z","uid":324594,"like":95,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6f09f53f37a590806f74251f865701afb24632a8","tid":1838753,"uid":324594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:40:50.000Z","msg":"我女朋友中左生死籤去做隔離營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要原來呢d籤唔係自己抽<br />\n都唔知係咪真係抽<br />\n<br />\n食屎狗政府，有事就醫護，無事就話人黑護。<br />\n心情落左谷底，佢月底應該就要去。<br />\n其實可以既話，真係寧願去果個係自己，<br />\n聽到佢講佢中左，真係喊左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我不斷叫佢罷工啦，call sick，又話咩做得護士，使命感，遇左會咁樣。<br />\n屌但係個政府當你 condom呢！"},{"pid":"a9d063e8276d8a4fbef482f841293fb3b7c622b1","tid":1838753,"uid":296491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:41:49.000Z","msg":"唔只佢，我地都應該一齊罷工！！！<br />\n<br />\n唔只醫護，應該全港大三罷！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1838722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1838722</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">與醫護同行，全港大三罷！</span></span>"},{"pid":"7cf88289322e835be6f0e6aacdcca15cf9526bd5","tid":1838753,"uid":324594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9d063e8276d8a4fbef482f841293fb3b7c622b1","tid":1838753,"uid":296491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:41:49.000Z","msg":"唔只佢，我地都應該一齊罷工！！！<br />\n<br />\n唔只醫護，應該全港大三罷！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1838722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1838722</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">與醫護同行，全港大三罷！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:43:56.000Z","msg":"如果其他人肯一齊罷，我諗都可以拉得郁佢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji